Wednesday, April 12, 2006
Random Stock Picks Generator The Random Stock Picker scans through a database of real stocks and generates 3 random stock picks. This is a great way to find some golden opportunities in a sea of stocks that you might not have considered before. You can also perform a symbol lookup of your choice using the search bar.
